---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="AI 情报日报 | Synapse Daily Intelligence">
  <section class="max-w-4xl mx-auto px-6 py-20">
    <p class="text-sm font-semibold tracking-widest text-[var(--color-accent)] uppercase mb-4">DAILY INTELLIGENCE</p>
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-extrabold text-white mb-4">AI 技术情报日报</h1>
    <p class="text-[var(--color-text)] text-lg mb-8">每天由 Synapse AI 团队自动生成 — 从海量 AI 动态中筛选出对企业管理者有实践价值的内容。</p>

    <!-- How it works -->
    <div class="bg-[var(--color-card)] border border-white/5 rounded-xl p-6 mb-10">
      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-white mb-4">情报是怎么生成的？</h2>
      <div class="font-mono text-sm text-[var(--color-text)] leading-loose">
        <p><span class="text-[var(--color-accent)]">8:00am</span> ── AI 技术研究员自动搜索 5 大 AI 前沿领域</p>
        <p><span class="text-[var(--color-accent)]">筛选</span> ──── 4 个标准过滤（实践可行/价值明确/成本可控/场景匹配）</p>
        <p><span class="text-[var(--color-accent)]">评审</span> ──── 智囊团内部审查（战略/决策/趋势三视角）</p>
        <p><span class="text-[var(--color-accent)]">产出</span> ──── 3-5 条精华发现 + 行动建议 + 当前工作关联分析</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Sample Topics -->
    <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-6">追踪领域</h2>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-4 mb-10">
      <div class="p-4 bg-[var(--color-card)] border border-white/5 rounded-lg">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm">Claude / Anthropic</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">Claude Code 更新、新功能、API变化</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 bg-[var(--color-card)] border border-white/5 rounded-lg">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm">AI Agent 框架</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">CrewAI / LangGraph / AutoGen 新进展</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 bg-[var(--color-card)] border border-white/5 rounded-lg">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm">Harness Engineering</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">Context Engineering 最佳实践</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 bg-[var(--color-card)] border border-white/5 rounded-lg">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm">AI 开发工具</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">Cursor / Claude Code / Copilot</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 bg-[var(--color-card)] border border-white/5 rounded-lg">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm">企业 AI 落地</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">真实效率提升案例</p>
      </div>
      <div class="p-4 bg-[var(--color-card)] border border-white/5 rounded-lg">
        <h3 class="font-semibold text-white text-sm">行业趋势</h3>
        <p class="text-xs text-[var(--color-muted)] mt-1">PropTech / 建筑AI / 市场动态</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- CTA -->
    <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-[var(--color-secondary)] to-[var(--color-primary)] rounded-xl p-8 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-white mb-2">想要定制你的行业情报？</h2>
      <p class="text-white/70 text-sm mb-4">Synapse 咨询客户可获得行业定制版每日情报服务。</p>
      <a href="/services" class="inline-block px-6 py-2 bg-[var(--color-accent)] text-[var(--color-dark)] rounded-lg font-bold text-sm hover:opacity-90 transition-opacity">了解咨询服务</a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
